<HEAD>Wildfires Destroy 138 Structures; 8,000 Evacuated</HEAD>
<NOTE>Eds: Leads with 10 grafs to UPDATE total evacuated during fire to
8,000 and include Smartville among evacuated towns, UPDATE with
emergency meeting of Yuba County supervisors, add that damage
