</TEXT>
<BYLINE>By The Associated Press</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
 Here is a sampling of recent foreign press comment on the <LOCATION> U.S. </LOCATION> presidential race between Democrat <PERSON> Michael </PERSON> <PERSON> Dukakis </PERSON> and Republican <PERSON> George </PERSON> <PERSON> Bush </PERSON>:
</TEXT>
