<HEAD>Fighting Leaves More Than 100 Salvadorans Dead or Wounded</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By DOUGLAS GRANT MINE</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>EL PARAISO, El Salvador (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
