 a sort of passing the reins along,'' said <ORGANIZATION> Playboy </ORGANIZATION> spokeswoman <PERSON> Robyn </PERSON> <PERSON> Radomski </PERSON>. `` In terms of where the company is now, it's a logical step. ... But <PERSON> Hef </PERSON> is still going to be editor-in-chief of the magazine and be involved in major strategic decisions.''
