<SECOND>BC-WPPSS Trial,0429</SECOND>
<HEAD>WPPSS Trial Resumes Wednesday; Another Utility Settles</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By JIM KLAHN</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>TUCSON, Ariz. (AP) </DATELINE>
